quran[60]{c,v,t}:
  51,1,"M wẽen ne sob-fugds fugb tεkẽ!"
  51,2,"La ne sawat nins sẽn yong ne koomɑ!"
  51,3,"La ne kogend nins sẽn zoet mõgrẽ wã,tɩ yɑɑ yol-yole."
  51,4,"La ne malεgs nins sẽn yaa yemsɑ yεlã pʋɩtba (ne Wẽnd sɑgelle)."
  51,5,"Ad b sẽn pʋlem yãmb bũmb ningã yaa sɩda."
  51,6,"La bãng tɩ yemsɑ Yaoobã na n yɩɩme."
  51,7,"La M wẽen ne saagã sẽn tar so-bugsã."
  51,8,"Ad yãmb ɑ Mɑk rãmbɑ y bee goam pʋgẽ sẽn kɩɩsd taaba."
  51,9,"Ned ning b sẽn wẽnems-a n yi sɩd-kũunɑ, yɑɑ b sẽn dɑ wẽng-ɑ soɑb Wẽnd minimã pʋgẽ, t'ɑ pɑ nɑ n kõ sɩd ye."
  51,10,"B kãaba zĩrimbe-rãmbã beedo."
  51,11,"B rãmb nins sẽn be bõrb pʋgẽ n yaa yam yaal-yaal rãmba."
  51,12,"B sokdame: ""Rolbã raar yaa ra-bʋre?"""
  51,13,"Raar ning bãmb sẽn be Bugum zugu, tɩ b zarbd-ba."
  51,14,"""Lemb-y yãmb nɑngã, yaa yãoã la bũmb ning yãmb sẽn da yɩ n yãgsd-ɑ wã""."
  51,15,"La ad wẽn-zoεtbã bee arzãn-rãmb la ko-nin pʋgẽ."
  51,16,"B yaa sẽn reegd bũmb ning b Soabã sẽn kõ-ba; ad bãmb rɑ yɑɑ manegdb taoor tɩ wã pa wa."
  51,17,"B ra yɩɩme n gõe bilf bal yʋng pʋgẽ."
  51,18,"La tõd-beed me, bãmb kota yaafa."
  51,19,"La bee bãmb arzεkã pʋgẽ bõaas pʋɩɩre, la b sẽn mong-a soab pʋɩɩre."
  51,20,"La tagmas-rãmb be tẽng zug ne bãng-n-wãak rãmba;"
  51,21,"La yãmb mensã me wɛɛngẽ. Yãmb pa tɑgsdẽ n getẽ?"
  51,22,"La be saasẽ wã, yãmb rɩtlã, la bũmb ning b sẽn pʋlem yãmbã."
  51,23,"M wẽen ne saag la Tẽng Soabã, ad a yaa sɩd wala yãmb sẽn gomdã."
  51,24,"Rẽ yĩnga a ɭbraahɩɩm sãan-waglã yẽsg waa fo nengẽ?"
  51,25,"Wakat ning b sẽn wa n kẽ a nengẽ n yeele: tɩlgre! T'a yeele:""yaa tɩlgre, yãmb yaa sãamba""."
  51,26,"T'a zãndg n kẽng a zakã rãmb nengẽ n tɩ wa ne lul-nobdga."
  51,27,"N pẽneg-a nebã n yeele: ""y pa na n rɩ?"""
  51,28,"(Lɑ b sẽn pɑ rɩtã) ɑ yɑeesɑ me n solg-b a yaεεsgã, tɩ b yeele: ""ra yaεεs ye""! La b noog a sũur ne biig sẽn yaa bãngda."
  51,29,"T'a pagã tool n kelem n wẽ a nengã n yeele: ""pʋg-yãan-kiri!"
  51,30,"Tɩ b yeele: ''yaa woto la fo Soabã yeel yã; ad Wẽnd la ɑ bʋʋd mita, n ya ɑ Bãngda''."
  51,31,"T'a (ɭbraahɩɩm) yeele: ''yãmb wa n na n maana bõe? Yaa yãmb Tẽn-tʋʋmba!"
  51,32,"Tɩ b yeele: ""ad b tʋma tõnd tɩ d kẽng nin-wẽnsẽ''"
  51,33,"Tɩ d tʋms b zug kug sẽn maan ne tãndo."
  51,34,"Sẽn ning tagmas fo Soabã nengẽ, mãan-n-zʋʋg rãmb yĩnga."
  51,35,"Tɩ Tõnd yiis ned ning sẽn ra be a (Tẽngã) pʋgẽ sẽn yaa muumin-rãmba."
  51,36,"La Tõnd pa mik a pʋgẽ, muumin-rãmb rẽnda zak a yembre."
  51,37,"La tõnd bas a pʋgẽ tagmase, neb nins sẽn yaεεsd naon-zabdgã yĩnga."
  51,38,"La a Muusa yellã pʋgẽ me, wakat ning Tõnd sẽn wa n tʋms-a a Fɩr-aoon nengẽ, ne yel-soalem sẽn vẽnege."
  51,39,"T'a balle n bɑs-bɑ n teeeg ɑ pãngã, n yeele: "" ɑ Musɑ yɑɑ tɩɩm soaba, ma gãeenga,(n gomd ɑ sẽn pɑ mi)"""
  51,40,"Tɩ Tõnd yõk-a ne a tãpã n fãeeg-b mogrã pʋgẽ, tɩ yẽnda yaa b sẽn sãbs-a soaba."
  51,41,"La a Aad yellã pʋgẽ me yel-soalem b ebe, wakat ning Tõnd sẽn wa n tʋms b zugu, seb-kĩrã."
  51,42,"A pa basd bũmb a sẽn ta a zug rẽndame t'a maan-a t'a lebg wa bugdu."
  51,43,"La a Ṯamuud yellã pʋgẽ, wakat ninga b sẽn wa n yeel-ba: ""wʋms-y noogo n tãag wakato"""
  51,44,"Tɩ b maan n zʋʋg n yi b Soabã sagelle, tɩ sa-tãsrã rɩk bãmb tɩ bãmb getẽ."
  51,45,"La b pa tõog n yik ye, b pa yɩ n paam sõngr me ye."
  51,46,"La a Nuuh nebã hal pĩnda, ad bãmb yɩɩme n yaa tar-n-yi Dĩin rãmba."
  51,47,"La saagã, Tõnd me-a lame ne pãnga, la ad Tõnd yaa ɑ kɩrmsɑ yalgdba."
  51,48,"La Tẽngã, Tõnd tẽeg-a lame, t'ɑ sɑkd zĩigɑ, la ɑd Tõnd lɑ Yalgdb sẽn be neere."
  51,49,"La bũmb fãa Tõnd naana kõbg a yiibu, sãnd-sãnde yãmb na tags n gese."
  51,50,"Bɩ y zoe n kẽng Wẽnd nengẽ, ad maam, m yaa bugsd sẽn vẽneg ne yãmb n yi-a."
  51,51,"La y ra maan soben-zẽng n lagem Wẽnd ye, ad maam, m yaa bugsd sẽn vẽneg ne yãmb n yi-A nɑngã."
  51,52,"Yaa woto bala, pa wa neb nins sẽn reng bãmb taoorã sẽn yaa tẽn-tʋʋma, rẽnda b yeele: ""yaa tɩɩm soaba, ma gãeenga"""
  51,53,"Rẽ yĩnga b sagenda taab ne-a-la (b sẽn yetã)? Pa woto ye, ad bãmb yaa neb sẽn yaa maan-n-zʋʋg rãmba."
  51,54,"Bɩ f ball n bas-b tɩ fo pa yɩ n yaa b sẽn sãbs-a soab ye."
  51,55,"La tẽeg tɩ ad tẽegrã nafda sɩd-kõtba."
  51,56,"La Mam pa naan zĩn-dãmbã la ninsaalbã, rẽnda b na tũ Maam yĩnga."
  51,57,"Mam pa rat rɩtl buud b nengẽ, M pa rat tɩ b rɩlg-M me ye."
  51,58,"Ad Wẽnde, Yẽ la rɩlgr Naaba, n yaa pãn-kεgeng Soaba."
  51,59,"La be ne neb nins sẽn wẽg-bã, naong pʋɩɩre, wala bãmb tũud-n-taasã pʋɩɩr bilgri, bɩ b ra yãg ye."
  51,60,"Rẽnd wɩɩbd be ne sẽn kɩfl-bã, bãmb raar ning b sẽn pʋlem-bã."
